					<h1>Coffee and Espresso</h1>
					
					<img src="/graphics/boyds.jpg" class="float-left" alt="" width="140" height="94" border="0" />
					
					<p>Boyds Coffee&reg; is the flagship brand of Boyd Coffee Company. That's why we pour all of our attention into making coffees that are sophisticated yet unassuming, elegant yet accessible. From popular favorites like Gourmet Medallion&reg; and Red Wagon&reg; Blend to swanky specialties like French No. 6&reg; and Rip City Coffee&reg;, we don't believe that world domination is an ingredient of a truly transcendent cup of coffee. Great coffee will always be great coffee. And great coffee will always be Boyds Coffee. Boyds Coffee's full range of blends satisfy preferences across the roasting spectrum, offering incredible tasting coffees that are smooth, lively or full-bodied and appropriately roasted to deliver the intended nuances of each selection. Boyds Coffee also offers single origin, proprietary blends, organics, Swiss-water® decaffeinated and other consumer-demanded coffees. Boyds Coffee ensures cup consistency, leading to customer satisfaction with each and every taste experience.</p>
					
