									<h3>Espresso, Cappucino and Iced Coffee</h3>
									
									<p><strong>Espresso</strong> - Our rare espresso blends are the result of an unmatched combination of coffee experience, skill, and technology. No roaster understands regional nuances better, blending exotic Indonesian Flavors, sweet Central American mellowness, vibrant African clarity, and rich Colombian consistency, to create balanced, smooth espressos that linger deliciously on the palate. Our European roasting system is the most sophisticated in the world, maintaining bean integrity and roast consistency. And our expertise in maintaining every aspect of selecting, roasting, blending, and brewing espresso assures you of all the full-bodied satisfaction you demand.</p>

									<p><strong>Syrups</strong> - Italia D’Oro authentic Italian syrups make every drink specialty. Italia D’Oro syrups are rich with the intense flavors that customers love. Formulated for optimal flavor impact when blended in coffee, espresso drinks, sodas, steamers, and even culinary specialties, Italia D'Oro syrups transform beverages to mouth-watering sensations. Housed in easy-to-handle and attractive square bottles, Italia D'Oro Syrups are the proven, easy way to create your own taste sensations.</p>
									
